      Cell[
       TextData["ControlledPower"]], 
      "paclet:QuantumMob/Q3/ref/ControlledPower", "QuantumMob Package Symbol"},
     "PackageLink",
     BaseStyle->{"DefinitionBox", CellFrame -> 0}], Cell[
    "Condrolled (or conditional) exponentiation", "TechNoteTableText",
     ExpressionUUID->"69ce5bfc-65e3-482a-a369-dd4ac864367a"]},
   {
    TemplateBox[{
      Cell[
       TextData["ContinuedFraction"]], "paclet:ref/ContinuedFraction"},
     "RefLink",
     BaseStyle->{"DefinitionBox", CellFrame -> 0}], Cell[
    "Generates the continued fraction representation of a number", 
     "TechNoteTableText",ExpressionUUID->
     "7ba7276a-65ec-4d38-a17b-299b018d89c3"]},
   {
