Cell["\<\
However, for the purpose of demonstration, we need to run the procedure \
(including the final measurement on the probe register). This can be achieve \
more efficiently by first calculating the output state right before the \
measurement and then performing the measurement repeatedly on the output \
state.\
\>", "TechNoteText",
 CellID->771976158,ExpressionUUID->"458de5a4-8ad0-4b5c-b5ab-804e8a9f8de8"],

